title: "Blonde Ambition" (w/ Dave Mizzoni)
itunes:title: "Blonde Ambition" (w/ Dave Mizzoni)
description:
It’s FAMILY in the studio today!

Fresh off getting his vocal polyps seared off and not speaking for 35 days, the incomparable Dave Mizzoni has returned to Las Culturistas to reveal his newly transformed voice. Spoiler alert: it's richer & smoother than you could ever imagine. And thank god, because the cultural discussions on today's docket deserve a voice like that. 

What's on the docket you ask? How 'bout Drag Race eliminations, Dua Lipa, Universal/Disney park developments, Handmaid’s Tale, sneak peaks at upcoming LIVE SHOWS with Matt, Bowen, and Dave...and that's just the tip of the iceberg. 

Plus, Sudi Green (or “friend that’s in the industry") phones in with some career advice on this week’s "Voice Mem-OH-you-bitch."
